Product review: Inside the box: phone, charger head, charger cable, SIM ejector. First setup went with no trouble. Performance: no problem in navigation speed. Appearance: simple black (for my variant). screen feels somewhat large. not much to say. Durability: plastic-covered back, feels durable enough for now. Battery Life: solid. 3% reduction per day for low-utilization personal usage. Software & OS: there are some bloatwares (probably around 5 apps), but removed without problem. Privacy: standard, no shutter for front-facing camera (solved by using sticker). Conncectivity: no problem with LTE. for NFC, cannot find the setting even though the logo exist. Fingerprint: good enough, works fine most of the time even though sometimes it is not accurate. Sound Quality: mostly contributed by down-firing speaker (no sound from upper speaker), which feels like mono audio. Verdict: For the price, this product fulfil my expectation. Not perfect, but solid. Seller review: Fast processing from seller. Product was on the way from seller in less than 3 hours. Simple packaging, but safe enough.
